# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                              :topic (e / economics)
                              :mod (v / vice))))

                  :ARG0 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (m3 / mission-01
                                    :ARG0 (c / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Taiwan"))
                                    :ARG1 (o / organization
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "World"
                                                :op2 "Trade"
                                                :op3 "Organization")))
                              :ARG2 (m4 / member)))
                  :ARG1 (m5 / mask
                        :mod (g / gas))
                  :ARG2 (t / they))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m6 / monday)))
      :snt2 b
      :ARG0 (p3 / person
            :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 m4))
      :source (p4 / person
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Nov."))
      :ARG1 m5
      :ARG2 t)

# ::alignments
(p / positive
      :domain (p2 / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Jason"
                  :op2 "Gillespie")
            :ARG0-of (b / bowl-01
                  :mod (p3 / pace)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday))
      :topic (p4 / prospect-02
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (o / overcome-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (s / setback
                              :mod (ii / injure-01
                                    :ARG1 p2)
                              :mod (l / last)))
                  :op2 (g / go-on-15
                        :ARG1 (t / tour-01
                              :ARG0 p2
                              :ARG1 (c / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Caribbean"))
                              :mod (c2 / cricket)
                              :duration (t2 / test
                                    :quant 4)
                              :time (m2 / month
                                    :mod (n3 / next)))))))

# ::alignments

      :ARG1 (p / province
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Venezuela"))
            :quant (s / several))
      :ARG3 (l / log-03
            :ARG1 (w / water))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (f2 / fall-01
                  :ARG1 (r2 / rain-01)
                  :time (d2 / day
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 5))
                  :ARG0-of (l2 / leave-13
                        :ARG1 (d3 / die-01
                              :ARG1 (p2 / person)))
                  :ARG0-of (c3 / cause-01
                        :ARG1 (t / tail-off-02
                              :ARG1 (e / evacuate-01
                                    :ARG1 (a / area
                                          :mod (s2 / seashore))))))))

                                    :op1 "Sierra"
                                    :op2 "Leone")))))
      :ARG1 (w / work-out-02
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (d / detail-01
                  :ARG1 (t / tribunal
                        :topic (c2 / crime-02
                              :ARG1 (w2 / war))
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / special-02)))
            :time (e / eve
                  :op1 (c3 / ceremony
                        :purpose (s3 / sign-02
                              :ARG0 a
                              :ARG1 (a2 / agree-01
                                    :ARG0-of (s4 / set-up-03
                                          :ARG1 (c4 / court
                                                :ARG1-of (w3 / wait-01
                                                      :time (w4 / wednesday))
                                                :ARG1-of (l / long-03)))))))))
